AR(Auto Regressive)

  • AR(1) \[ y_t = c+ \phi_1 y_{t-1}+\epsilon_t, \ \ \epsilon_t \sim N(0,\sigma^2) \]
  • AR(p) \[ y_t = c+ \sum_{i=1}^p \phi_i y_{t-i}+\epsilon_t, \ \ \epsilon_t \sim N(0,\sigma^2) \]

\(B\).

\[By_t=y_{t-1}\]

,ARIMA\((1,0,1)\) \(y_t=\phi_1y_{t-1}+\theta_1\epsilon_{t-1}+\epsilon_{t}\)

\[ y_t=\phi_1By_{t}+\theta_1B\epsilon_{t}+\epsilon_{t}\\ \Leftrightarrow \ (1-\phi_1B)y_t=(1+\theta_1B)\epsilon_t. \]

\[ \Delta y_t=(1-B)y_t \]

\[ \Delta^2 y_t = (1-B)^2y_t = (1-B)(y_t-y_{t-1})\\ =(y_t-y_{t-1})-(y_{t-1}-y_{t-2}) \]

d\(\Delta^dy_t\)

ARIMA(p,d,q)\(\Delta^dy_t\)ARMA(p,q)

\[ \left(1-\sum_{i=1}^p\phi_iB^i\right)\Delta^dy_t=\left(1+\sum_{j=1}^q\theta_jB^j\right)\epsilon_t \]

\[ \phi(B)\Delta^dy_t=\theta(B)\epsilon_t \]

.

\(D\)\(\Delta_x^Dy_t\)SARIMA(0,0,0)(P,D,Q)[s]

\[ \left(1-\sum_{I=1}^P\Phi_IB^{sI}\right)\Delta_s^Dy_t=\left(1+\sum_{J=1}^Q\Theta_JB^{SJ}\right)\epsilon_t \]

ARIMASARIMA(p,d,q)(P,D,Q)[s]

\[ \left(1-\sum_{i=1}^p\phi_iB^i\right)\left(1-\sum_{I=1}^P\Phi_IB^{sI}\right)\Delta^d\Delta_s^Dy_t=\left(1+\sum_{j=1}^q\theta_jB^j\right)\left(1+\sum_{J=1}^Q\Theta_JB^{SJ}\right)\epsilon_t \]

ARIMA(SARIMAX)

petro_law <- Seatbelts[,c("PetrolPrice","law")]
model_sarimax <- Arima(
  y = Seatbelts[,"front"],
  order = c(1,1,1),
  seasonal = list(order=c(1,0,0)),
  xreg = petro_law
)
